[[twgist|https://github.com/PotOfCoffee2Go/twgist]] is a [[Command-line Interface (CLI)|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Command-line_interface]] tool which uses [[TiddlyWiki|https://tiddlywiki.com]] and [[Git|https://git-scm.com]] commands to store 'server' edition [[TiddlyWiki on Node.js|https://tiddlywiki.com/static/Installing%2520TiddlyWiki%2520on%2520Node.js.html]] tiddlers in [[GitHub|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GitHub]] [[Gists|https://github.com]] or GitHub [[Repositories|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Repository_(version_control)]].

The CLI simplifies the commands required to init, edit, pull, and push wiki tiddlers to GitHub by performing TiddlyWiki and Git commands on your behalf.

